Burgundy Private, Private Banking by Axis Bank, hosted an evening steeped in rhythm and heritage with Parampara – The Joy of Music by Shankar Mahadevan, in partnership with the #NitaMukeshAmbaniCulturalCentre.
Our clients were immersed in an unforgettable celebration of Indian classical and contemporary music, brought to life by the maestro himself and an ensemble of his sons and students, celebrating the guru-shishya parampara. 
This event was part of #BurgundyPrivateExperiences, a curated collection of arts, culture, insights, and lifestyle experiences crafted for our esteemed clientele.

To learn more about Burgundy Private, please visit axisbank.com/burgundyprivate. We would be delighted to speak with you.

#burgundyprivate #axisbank #nmacc
